author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Gubernija Says 2017 Loss Of 12 Months Without Tax Deduction Up Eur 0.646 Million
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - Gubernija Ab:
* INTERIM INFORMATION FOR TWELVE MONTHS OF 2017 * SAYS UNAUDITED REVENUE IN 2017 INCOME MADE EUR 7.454 MILLION, IN 2016 INCOME WAS EUR 8.184 MILLION
* SAYS COMPANYâ€˜S EBITDA IN 2017 WAS THOUSAND 5.3 EUR, IN 2016 IT WAS EUR 158 THOUSAND
* SAYS 2017 LOSS OF TWELVE MONTHS WITHOUT TAX DEDUCTION MADE EUR 0.646 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
